rgued. (The Guardian)//<br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ1 : 簽咗咁多聯署 / 英國佬唔會幫我地 /英國佬都唔想收咁多新移民喇 / 英國佬講咗咁耐都冇做過嘢 簽嚟都冇用<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗1分鐘搞掂又冇成本嘅嘢點解唔做咗先 <br />\n<br />\n六合彩咁難中你又買?<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n今次係有下議會議員帶頭講要俾full citizenship BNO holder<br />\n10萬人都簽唔到叫人地點幫你啊<br />\n我地要送子彈啊<br />\n<br />\nQ2: 好多97後都冇BNO 我地唔可以扔低佢地<br />\n<br />\nA: 有BC又有幾多人會即刻走 <br />\n反而有咗後路可以更盡情咁去抗爭<br />\n同埋到時大量英國國民喺香港 （ ff住先）可以增加英國嘅談判籌碼<br />\n真係去到最壞情況都可以諗方法帶埋d細路走<br />\n<br />\nQ3: 佢要tick Only British citizens or UK residents have the right to sign<br />\n我 得 / 冇BNO簽唔簽得？<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗verify citizenship 自己諗簽唔簽<br />\n只要提供 email address + 英文名 ＋選Location + Postal code<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅take返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打000000 或 N/A<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPElNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=86f9b3a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自己一個簽係唔夠 請share出去<br />\n例如：<br />\nLib Dem<br />\nJo Swinson<br />\n各大香港英國報章<br />\nTwitter<br />\nInstagram<br />\n英國MPs"},{"pid":"4b7e762ab7782bb1ccc7644ed4009b1b7d461a39","tid":1476284,"uid":14979,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T00:46:05.000Z","msg":"個句「胡椒噴霧呀胡椒彈」令我諗起「你阿媽個波罩你」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n哥哥姐姐咁努力都係為左你地大個唔洗好似我地咁出黎抗爭咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e2691975dbb2766a50e74c980e413601b1eadf","tid":1476284,"uid":156666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T00:48:25.000Z","msg":"會唔會比藍絲起底架... 班人咁鍾意搞小朋友"},{"pid":"ca6a5a342e362e4a2f36caef24e4bb80417299c3","tid":1476284,"uid":87367,"li